generic:link.msg:message: Identity "Value of Total pending reconciliation" = (Over 3 months and upto 6 months + Over 6 months and upto 12 months + Over 1 year and upto 2 years + Over 2 years ) do not tally

Identity "Value of Total of all maurity bucket" = ((1 - 28 days)+(29 days and upto 3 months)+(Over 3 months and upto 6 months)+(Over 6 months and upto 1 year)+(Over1 year and upto 3 years)+(Over 3 years and upto 5 years)+(Over 5 years) +(Non-Sensitive)) do not tally
"Cumulative gap for (1-28 Days)"should be equal to "Net gap for (1-28 Days)"
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (29 days to 3 months) " = (Cumulative gap (1 to 28 Days) + Net gap (29 days to 3 months)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (3 Months to 6 Months) " = (Cumulative gap (29 Days to 3 Months) + Net gap (3 Months to 6 Months)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (6 Months to 1 Year)" = (Cumulative gap (3 Months to 6 Months) + Net gap (6 Months to 1 Year)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (1 Year to 3 Years) " = (Cumulative gap (6 Months to 1 Year) + Net gap (1 Year to 3 Years)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (3 Years to 5 Years) " = (Cumulative gap (1 Year to 3 Years) + Net gap (3 Years to 5 Years)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (Over 5 Years)" = (Cumulative gap (3 Years to 5 Years) + Net gap(Over 5 Years)) do not tally
Identity "Value of Cumulative gap (Non-Sensitive)" = (Cumulative gap (Over 5 Years) + Net gap(Non-Sensitive)) do not tally
" Net gap as % of Assets" should be equal to "Net Gap/Assets"
If value "Assets" is less than or equal to 0 then "Net Gap as % of Assets" should be equal to 0
"Cumulative gap Total" should be equal to "Cumulative gap (Non-Sensitive)"
Identity "Value of Total pending reconciliation" = (Over 3 months and upto 6 months + Over 6 months and upto 12 months + Over 1 year and upto 2 years + Over 2 years ) do not tally
